no matter what you look like,

289
00:12:57,480 --> 00:12:58,879
my feelings for you remain the same.

290
00:12:59,559 --> 00:13:00,440
As long as I'm by your side,

291
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:01,679
I get nervous.

292
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,720
Whenever you look at me, I...

293
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,320
I... I just want to run away.

294
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:08,399
Are you that afraid of me?

295
00:13:08,639 --> 00:13:09,240
It's not fear.

296
00:13:09,519 --> 00:13:09,840
It's...

297
00:13:10,679 --> 00:13:11,480
it's that I care.

298
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,440
I'm not forcing you to accept me.

299
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,879
I fully respect if you don't accept me.

300
00:13:17,679 --> 00:13:18,360
I just want to

301
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,120
tell you how I feel.

302
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:22,919
Guifang.

303
00:13:24,039 --> 00:13:25,639
Your bravery and fearlessness have always inspired me.

304
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:26,759
Being by your side,

305
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:28,720
I've become fearless just like you.

306
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:33,240
How long did you spend memorizing those lines?

307
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,320
Fearless?

308
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:40,039
Because mothers are strong.

309
00:13:44,639 --> 00:13:45,120
Guifang.

310
00:13:45,919 --> 00:13:46,320
Fang'er.

311
00:13:46,639 --> 00:13:47,799
Professor Wang just called.

312
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,559
There's a problem with the seedlings sold a few days ago.

313
00:13:50,679 --> 00:13:51,759
The two grad students sent to guide them

314
00:13:51,759 --> 00:13:52,600
can't solve it.

315
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,200
There's a typhoon in Hainan right now.

316
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,360
Professor Wang is stuck there.

317
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:56,679
Right now, other than her,

318
00:13:56,679 --> 00:13:57,960
you're the only one who understands the situation.

319
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,879
If we delay another three or four days,

320
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,519
millions worth of seedlings will be ruined.

321
00:14:09,639 --> 00:14:11,279
We've seen pretty much everything we came to see.

322
00:14:12,519 --> 00:14:13,200
Let's go back.

323
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,679
Godmother is willing to go back with us.

324
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,080
That's a good thing.

325
00:14:22,519 --> 00:14:24,000
Company isn't a cure-all.

326
00:14:25,039 --> 00:14:26,480
And traveling can't solve problems either.

327
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,679
She hasn't turned young at all.

328
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:29,960
This proves

329
00:14:30,879 --> 00:14:32,000
she still has no will to live.

330
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,480
Let's think of another way then.

331
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:58,080
A Fu, you...

332
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:05,840
Xiaocan!

333
00:15:09,519 --> 00:15:10,080
Xiaocan!

334
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:16,039
What's wrong? What's wrong?

335
00:15:16,039 --> 00:15:17,440
I just saw Xiaocan.

336
00:15:18,519 --> 00:15:19,600
He fell right from up there.

337
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:21,320
And he... he shouted "A Fu".

338
00:15:21,799 --> 00:15:22,879
In the blink of an eye, he was gone.

339
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,720
Where did he run off to?

340
00:15:23,799 --> 00:15:24,600
What's wrong? What's wrong, Godmother? Godmother?

341
00:15:24,639 --> 00:15:25,240
What happened? What happened?

342
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,399
I just saw Xiaocan.

343
00:15:26,639 --> 00:15:27,840
He fell right from up there.

344
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,320
And he shouted "A Fu".

345
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:30,600
I... I don't know

346
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,000
how he just disappeared in the blink of an eye.

347
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:32,720
Is it this one?

348
00:15:32,919 --> 00:15:33,679
Isn't he right here?

349
00:15:33,799 --> 00:15:34,840
Not me... not him.

350
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,080
I really saw Xiaocan.

351
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:36,360
Godmother.

352
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,600
And he shouted "A Fu".

353
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:38,480
Xiaocan isn't here anymore.

354
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:39,080
What do you mean Xiaocan isn't here?

355
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:39,840
Didn't you say he's gone?

356
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:40,320
Don't worry.

357
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,200
How could it not be him?

358
00:15:41,200 --> 00:15:42,159
I saw him with my own eyes.

359
00:15:42,159 --> 00:15:42,799
How could it not?

360
00:15:42,799 --> 00:15:44,279
How is it not him? Godmother, calm down.

361
00:15:44,279 --> 00:15:45,039
Xiaocan is no longer here.

362
00:15:45,039 --> 00:15:45,960
Don't you already know that?

363
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:46,879
You know he's gone.

364
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:47,320
That's right.

365
00:15:47,799 --> 00:15:48,879
I can't explain it to you.

366
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:50,480
Fang'er... Godmother...

367
00:15:51,399 --> 00:15:51,720
Godmother.

368
00:15:51,720 --> 00:15:52,759
Get away, get away!

369
00:15:52,759 --> 00:15:53,759
Stop bothering me!

370
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:56,320
Sister Rui, can you still contact that A Fu?

371
00:15:56,679 --> 00:15:58,759
I haven't been able to find him since the funeral.

372
00:15:58,759 --> 00:16:00,240
Ma Jianfei, pick up, pick up.

373
00:16:00,639 --> 00:16:02,360
Ma Jianfei, Ma Jianfei, pick up the phone.

374
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:04,440
I really just saw him.

375
00:16:05,159 --> 00:16:06,600
He fell right from up there.

376
00:16:07,240 --> 00:16:09,080
Why can't any of you hear it?

377
00:17:54,559 --> 00:17:54,960
Guifang

378
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:55,519
Who is that?

379
00:17:55,799 --> 00:17:57,759
It seems to be Godmother's former colleague, Auntie Niu.

380
00:17:57,759 --> 00:17:58,880
It really is you.

381
00:17:58,920 --> 00:17:59,799
Auntie Niu, hello.

382
00:18:00,079 --> 00:18:01,519
Long time no see.

383
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,400
How is your illness?

384
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:07,000
I'm fully recovered.

385
00:18:07,079 --> 00:18:08,200
Fully recovered.

386
00:18:09,079 --> 00:18:11,119
You had pancreatic cancer.

387
00:18:13,240 --> 00:18:14,279
Your son is capable.

388
00:18:15,279 --> 00:18:17,920
Right, right, right. You raised a good son.

389
00:18:18,559 --> 00:18:20,279
I said so back then.

390
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:22,160
Xiaocan is promising.

391
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:24,039
He'll definitely have a great future.

392
00:18:24,039 --> 00:18:26,519
Even though he didn't get to study in Belgium.

393
00:18:26,799 --> 00:18:28,519
But he cured your illness.

394
00:18:29,079 --> 00:18:29,839
That's great.

395
00:18:30,559 --> 00:18:31,119
Look at you now.

396
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:32,599
You're younger than before.

397
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,319
Like a career woman.

398
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:35,680
That's great.

399
00:18:36,359 --> 00:18:37,440
How are you doing now?

400
00:18:37,920 --> 00:18:38,359
Me?

401
00:18:40,000 --> 00:18:41,039
Don't even ask about me.

402
00:18:41,519 --> 00:18:42,480
To tell you the truth.

403
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:44,319
I have rectal cancer.

404
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:45,960
But it's okay.

405
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,000
It's still in the early stages.

406
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:47,799
It's fine.

407
00:18:48,559 --> 00:18:51,119
I have no children and no partner in this life.

408
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:53,119
I use the best medicine.

409
00:18:53,359 --> 00:18:55,039
I spend money freely.

410
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:57,759
My biggest wish before I die...

411
00:18:58,599 --> 00:18:59,960
...is to live in a new house.

412
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:00,359
Look.

413
00:19:01,039 --> 00:19:02,240
This is the new house I bought.

414
00:19:02,279 --> 00:19:04,519
120 square meters, large three-bedroom. It's wonderful.

415
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:05,720
Come, let's go up and take a look.

416
00:19:06,359 --> 00:19:07,799
Maybe another day. I have things to do.

417
00:19:08,079 --> 00:19:09,039
What other day?

418
00:19:09,039 --> 00:19:10,880
How many more times can we meet?

419
00:19:11,119 --> 00:19:13,519
Another day means seeing me at the funeral.

420
00:19:13,839 --> 00:19:14,799
Come on, come on. Really.

421
00:19:15,079 --> 00:19:16,759
I really missed you.

422
00:19:16,839 --> 00:19:17,640
Missed you to death.

423
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:21,640
Reporting in.

424
00:19:21,759 --> 00:19:22,640
Fang'er is safe now.

425
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,960
She went to Auntie Niu's house. Don't worry.

426
00:19:27,440 --> 00:19:27,920
It's right here.

427
00:19:28,519 --> 00:19:29,319
Number 02.

428
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:31,480
Xiao Guan.

429
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:33,400
Auntie Niu is here.

430
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:35,000
Bro, bro, bro, stop working, stop working.

431
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,880
Don't hurt Auntie Niu and this sister.

432
00:19:37,039 --> 00:19:38,119
Let me introduce you.

433
00:19:38,359 --> 00:19:40,079
This is our contractor, Xiao Guan.

434
00:19:40,759 --> 00:19:42,279
This is my good friend.

435
00:19:42,599 --> 00:19:44,079
My closest sister.

436
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,240
Sister, hello, hello.

437
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,079
Call her Auntie.

438
00:19:47,279 --> 00:19:49,039
You're too young, Auntie.

439
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:50,599
You've maintained yourself so well.

440
00:19:51,079 --> 00:19:51,400
Come.

441
00:19:51,519 --> 00:19:52,079
Look around.

442
00:19:52,119 --> 00:19:52,960
Feel free to look around.

443
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:54,200
The wall putty is all done.

444
00:19:54,599 --> 00:19:56,480
The ceiling, the ceiling, the ceiling isn't done yet.

445
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:59,319
Auntie Niu, living here alone will be very comfortable.

446
00:20:01,599 --> 00:20:02,359
The view is pretty good.

447
00:20:02,359 --> 00:20:03,359
You can even see the mountains.

448
00:20:04,599 --> 00:20:05,279
Let me tell you.

449
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:08,279
As soon as I came here, I set my eyes on this unit.

450
00:20:08,279 --> 00:20:09,640
Auntie Niu has great taste.

451
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,599
Look, surrounded by mountains on all sides.

452
00:20:12,079 --> 00:20:13,960
The breeze will be so cool at night.

453
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,200
If you think the breeze isn't enough...

454
00:20:15,519 --> 00:20:16,799
...we'll install a fan here for you.

455
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,680
360-degree circulation.

456
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:20,799
When the time comes, make sure the tiles...

457
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,079
...are done beautifully for me.

458
00:20:22,079 --> 00:20:22,440
Sure.

459
00:20:22,839 --> 00:20:23,400
Right here...

460
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,200
...we'll put a small table.

461
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:27,039
Eating sunflower seeds, chatting, how nice.

462
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:29,200
So beautiful, I can picture it already.

463
00:20:30,119 --> 00:20:32,640
What's the estimated budget for this renovation?

464
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:35,359
Including labor and materials, about 350,000.

465
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:36,480
That expensive?

466
00:20:36,799 --> 00:20:37,799
Expensive? Not at all.

467
00:20:38,359 --> 00:20:39,599
This is a friendly price.

468
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,880
I use big brands, good materials.

469
00:20:43,000 --> 00:20:43,920
Auntie Niu, rest assured.

470
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:45,480
Every penny will be spent where it counts.

471
00:20:45,599 --> 00:20:46,640
Refund the excess, make up the shortage.

472
00:20:46,799 --> 00:20:47,480
No problem.

473
00:20:48,079 --> 00:20:49,039
Quite a few rooms.

474
00:20:51,319 --> 00:20:52,519
These are all big bay windows.

475
00:20:52,599 --> 00:20:53,039
Right.

476
00:20:53,279 --> 00:20:54,519
Pretty good. Bay windows are great.

477
00:20:54,519 --> 00:20:54,960
When it's done...

478
00:20:55,599 --> 00:20:56,960
...I'll save a room for you.

479
00:20:57,200 --> 00:20:58,680
You have to come stay here.

480
00:20:59,319 --> 00:21:00,119
Auntie is staying here too?

481
00:21:00,119 --> 00:21:00,920
Of course.

482
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:03,240
Tell me what style you like then.

483
00:21:03,440 --> 00:21:04,759
I'll design it for you.

484
00:21:05,039 --> 00:21:05,920
It's all within the budget.

485
00:21:06,519 --> 00:21:07,880
Give some suggestions.

486
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:11,240
Xiao Guan, bring your design blueprints...

487
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:13,279
...or the renderings for me to see.

488
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:13,799
Don't have any.

489
00:21:15,039 --> 00:21:16,519
It's all in my head.

490
00:21:17,119 --> 00:21:18,440
Who needs design plans?

491
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:20,720
I've already imagined the scene.

492
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:22,119
It's... it's all in my brain.

493
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:24,359
You've got some nerve.

494
00:21:24,359 --> 00:21:25,519
You don't even have a design plan...

495
00:21:25,519 --> 00:21:27,400
...and you dare to start marking lines?

496
00:21:27,519 --> 00:21:29,000
Don't talk about that. Auntie Niu knows.

497
00:21:29,079 --> 00:21:31,599
I'm famous in the renovation world for my smart brain.

498
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:32,519
Let me tell you.

499
00:21:32,519 --> 00:21:35,160
He's renovated over a dozen units in this building.

500
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:36,000
Yes, don't mention it.

501
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:36,839
Apartments over 200 square meters...

502
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:37,799
...I drew them all by hand.

503
00:21:37,920 --> 00:21:38,920
Then do you have the purchase list?

504
00:21:39,039 --> 00:21:39,400
No.

505
00:21:39,960 --> 00:21:41,319
It's all in my head.

506
00:21:41,720 --> 00:21:43,559
No purchase list?

507
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:44,359
Purchase list...

508
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:45,200
This brain...

509
00:21:45,279 --> 00:21:45,920
Yes, yes, yes.

510
00:21:45,920 --> 00:21:46,359
Wait a moment.

511
00:21:46,359 --> 00:21:47,920
How can you not have that?

512
00:21:51,119 --> 00:21:52,680
Of course there is, Auntie Niu.

513
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:55,640
You have to remember the details.

514
00:21:55,640 --> 00:21:58,000
Don't worry, we've gone over all this.

515
00:21:58,720 --> 00:21:59,279
I'm telling you,

516
00:21:59,279 --> 00:22:00,720
when the time comes, the glue...

517
00:22:00,880 --> 00:22:02,359
has to be the best kind.

518
00:22:02,359 --> 00:22:03,559
Because otherwise I...

519
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:04,440
Don't you worry.

520
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:05,640
I'll use all natural stuff for you.

521
00:22:05,839 --> 00:22:06,480
It won't smell at all.

522
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:07,680
Auntie Niu, no need to see me out.

523
00:22:08,799 --> 00:22:11,960
It's fine. I'm relieved to see you doing well.

524
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:14,640
Come visit often when you're free.

525
00:22:14,759 --> 00:22:15,079
Okay.

526
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:17,200
Treat this place like your own home.

527
00:22:17,640 --> 00:22:19,000
Okay. Take care of yourself.

528
00:22:19,559 --> 00:22:20,200
Okay, sure.

529
00:22:20,359 --> 00:22:20,839
Goodbye.

530
00:22:21,440 --> 00:22:22,079
Take care.

531
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:24,799
Bye.

532
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:31,480
Auntie Niu.

533
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:35,519
How about I oversee the renovation for you?

534
00:22:36,079 --> 00:22:36,880
No need for that.

535
00:22:37,519 --> 00:22:39,079
You've just recovered from a serious illness.

536
00:22:39,079 --> 00:22:40,480
You should just focus on resting.

537
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,680
Don't be so polite with me.

538
00:22:42,519 --> 00:22:43,480
Just focus on your treatment.

539
00:22:44,559 --> 00:22:45,599
Nothing matters more than your life.

540
00:22:49,559 --> 00:22:49,920
Okay.

541
00:22:56,079 --> 00:22:57,680
We'll have to make do with this for now.

542
00:22:57,880 --> 00:22:58,920
Fang'er, you sleep on this.

543
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:00,640
The pillow with the most flowers.

544
00:23:01,079 --> 00:23:02,759
This flowery quilt is yours too.

545
00:23:02,920 --> 00:23:03,359
Right.

546
00:23:29,960 --> 00:23:30,559
Time to get up.

547
00:23:31,359 --> 00:23:31,720
Hurry up.

548
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:32,519
Xiao Yin.

549
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:33,359
Xixi.

550
00:23:33,839 --> 00:23:34,640
Wake up, wake up.

551
00:23:42,519 --> 00:23:42,839
Fang'er.

552
00:23:44,119 --> 00:23:45,279
Come on, come on.

553
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:53,640
These wires...

554
00:23:54,079 --> 00:23:55,839
we need to redesign them later.

555
00:23:56,279 --> 00:23:57,200
They can't be crossed like that.

556
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:58,119
That would be very dangerous.

557
00:23:58,319 --> 00:23:58,839
Don't worry.

558
00:23:58,839 --> 00:23:59,640
It's all in my head.

559
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:01,599
And the waterproofing for the kitchen and bathroom...

560
00:24:01,599 --> 00:24:02,559
we must apply a few extra layers.

561
00:24:02,559 --> 00:24:04,039
Leaking downstairs would be a huge hassle.

562
00:24:04,559 --> 00:24:05,519
It's all in my head.

563
00:24:05,799 --> 00:24:07,640
Should the floor heating go through the kitchen or the bathroom?

564
00:24:07,640 --> 00:24:08,720
We'll design that later.

565
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:09,960
Over here, I want to put a...

566
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:11,799
...floor-standing air conditioner for her.

567
00:24:12,079 --> 00:24:13,039
Wait, wait a sec, Sister.

568
