00:53:13,719 --> 00:53:15,760
It is said that the laboratory you two collaborated on...

1130
00:53:15,760 --> 00:53:17,719
...is to make technical contributions to the development of the West.

1131
00:53:18,159 --> 00:53:19,199
So, when did you two...

1132
00:53:19,199 --> 00:53:20,119
...decide to collaborate?

1133
00:53:20,280 --> 00:53:21,719
And I heard that you two were classmates.

1134
00:53:22,280 --> 00:53:23,679
Do you have any stories to share?

1135
00:53:26,360 --> 00:53:26,760
Yes.

1136
00:53:27,360 --> 00:53:29,239
We have many stories of fighting side by side.

1137
00:53:31,039 --> 00:53:32,880
We are comrades willing to strive...

1138
00:53:32,920 --> 00:53:33,800
...all our lives for the cause of agriculture.

1139
00:53:34,960 --> 00:53:35,360
Good.

1140
00:53:37,920 --> 00:53:38,840
Dean, do you have anything...

1141
00:53:38,840 --> 00:53:40,119
...you want to say to the two professors?

1142
00:53:40,639 --> 00:53:42,320
Thanks to our Professor Wei this time.

1143
00:54:16,159 --> 00:54:17,679
That cold buffet they prepared...

1144
00:54:17,800 --> 00:54:18,679
...really didn't have anything good to eat.

1145
00:54:19,119 --> 00:54:20,199
Your cooking is still the best.

1146
00:54:21,159 --> 00:54:22,159
If you like it...

1147
00:54:22,159 --> 00:54:23,199
...come over and eat often when you have time.

1148
00:54:23,599 --> 00:54:24,719
Here, eat this egg.

1149
00:54:28,800 --> 00:54:29,159
By the way.

1150
00:54:30,079 --> 00:54:31,000
How is your hometown?

1151
00:54:31,320 --> 00:54:32,920
The families have all built greenhouses.

1152
00:54:33,239 --> 00:54:34,400
They're no longer afraid of bad weather.

1153
00:54:35,320 --> 00:54:37,719
The villagers' lives are finally getting better and better.

1154
00:54:38,320 --> 00:54:38,800
No wonder.

1155
00:54:39,800 --> 00:54:41,480
When I went there for inspection last time...

1156
00:54:41,760 --> 00:54:43,760
...I saw your village has turned into multi-story houses.

1157
00:54:44,320 --> 00:54:46,239
The changes are truly earth-shattering compared to before.

1158
00:54:46,400 --> 00:54:47,280
This is just the beginning.

1159
00:54:48,039 --> 00:54:49,920
Our lives will be even better in the future.

1160
00:54:52,400 --> 00:54:54,239
I'm going to sweep Xiaocan's grave tomorrow.

1161
00:54:54,360 --> 00:54:54,840
Are you going?

1162
00:54:56,480 --> 00:54:57,239
I can't make it tomorrow.

1163
00:54:57,719 --> 00:54:59,079
I have an early flight to Qinghai tomorrow morning.

1164
00:55:00,039 --> 00:55:01,719
How about I go with you again when I get back?

1165
00:55:02,760 --> 00:55:03,119
Okay.

1166
00:55:03,719 --> 00:55:04,039
Good.

1167
00:55:04,239 --> 00:55:04,599
Eat up.

1168
00:55:22,360 --> 00:55:23,000
You...

1169
00:55:24,119 --> 00:55:26,199
You always come and go in a hurry.

1170
00:55:27,440 --> 00:55:29,360
Mom has so many things I didn't get to tell you.

1171
00:55:31,800 --> 00:55:32,840
Li Wai's child...

1172
00:55:33,559 --> 00:55:34,760
...is in kindergarten now.

1173
00:55:35,559 --> 00:55:37,159
That little Ao Tian is very naughty.

1174
00:55:37,719 --> 00:55:38,719
All day long in kindergarten...

1175
00:55:38,719 --> 00:55:40,239
...he steals snacks from other kids.

1176
00:55:42,079 --> 00:55:44,159
Now whenever Xiao Yin hears the kindergarten calling...

1177
00:55:44,159 --> 00:55:45,159
...she doesn't dare to answer.

1178
00:55:45,360 --> 00:55:47,280
It must be that little Ao Tian causing trouble again.

1179
00:55:50,159 --> 00:55:50,960
As for Xiao Rui...

1180
00:55:53,320 --> 00:55:54,599
...she is very happy after marriage.

1181
00:55:57,079 --> 00:55:58,599
I heard a while ago that she's pregnant.

1182
00:56:00,199 --> 00:56:01,440
The child she gives birth to...

1183
00:56:02,239 --> 00:56:03,280
...will definitely look like her.

1184
00:56:03,519 --> 00:56:04,639
Just as beautiful as she is.

1185
00:56:06,679 --> 00:56:07,239
As for Mom...

1186
00:56:08,440 --> 00:56:09,400
...you don't need to worry.

1187
00:56:10,880 --> 00:56:11,800
Mom now...

1188
00:56:12,599 --> 00:56:14,320
...has a laboratory of her own.

1189
00:56:15,519 --> 00:56:17,559
Everyone calls me Professor Kong now.

1190
00:56:19,480 --> 00:56:20,639
It still sounds a bit unfamiliar to me.

1191
00:56:22,719 --> 00:56:23,079
By the way.

1192
00:56:23,800 --> 00:56:26,519
Your place here is classified as an illegal structure.

1193
00:56:28,000 --> 00:56:29,760
Looking around this whole area...

1194
00:56:31,159 --> 00:56:32,239
...yours is the most conspicuous.

1195
00:56:33,480 --> 00:56:34,280
Later on, Mom...

1196
00:56:34,440 --> 00:56:35,840
...will change it to one that's not so conspicuous for you.

1197
00:56:36,559 --> 00:56:37,000
Be good.

1198
00:56:53,280 --> 00:56:54,960
By the way, how is it going with Kong Guifang?

1199
00:56:55,800 --> 00:56:56,280
Sir.

1200
00:56:57,079 --> 00:56:58,400
Kong Guifang is now...

1201
00:56:58,400 --> 00:57:00,239
...no longer restricted by the twenty-five-year contract.

1202
00:57:00,719 --> 00:57:02,679
As long as she doesn't court death now...

1203
00:57:03,079 --> 00:57:04,559
...she will definitely live until she dies.

1204
00:57:04,960 --> 00:57:05,719
She can live to old age.

1205
00:57:06,280 --> 00:57:06,679
Very good.

1206
00:57:07,400 --> 00:57:08,320
We must maintain...

1207
00:57:08,320 --> 00:57:09,719
...this distinguished client of ours well.

1208
00:57:10,039 --> 00:57:10,400
Yes, sir.

1209
00:57:55,760 --> 00:57:56,159
Mom

1210
00:57:57,199 --> 00:57:58,400
These flowers are blooming really well

1211
00:58:02,280 --> 00:58:03,320
These sunflowers

1212
00:58:03,880 --> 00:58:06,519
are a new hybrid experiment Mom's done these past two years

1213
00:58:07,800 --> 00:58:09,760
Even in the harshest environments

1214
00:58:09,760 --> 00:58:11,400
they are easy to plant and grow

1215
00:58:13,199 --> 00:58:14,519
I believe these flowers

1216
00:58:15,199 --> 00:58:17,679
will become seeds that change the world

1217
00:58:18,639 --> 00:58:20,079
Mom, you're really amazing right now

1218
00:58:20,599 --> 00:58:22,360
You've accomplished another big thing, really

1219
00:58:23,079 --> 00:58:24,840
You should hurry and record this technology

1220
00:58:25,360 --> 00:58:26,280
spread it around

1221
00:58:26,280 --> 00:58:27,239
and benefit everyone

1222
00:58:27,559 --> 00:58:29,000
Make a "Sunflower Manual" out of it

1223
00:58:30,079 --> 00:58:31,559
What are you talking about?

1224
00:58:32,719 --> 00:58:33,840
I know, my mom's

1225
00:58:33,840 --> 00:58:35,519
planting sunflowers must be very meaningful

1226
00:58:36,159 --> 00:58:37,400
Sunflowers are full of vitality

1227
00:58:37,559 --> 00:58:38,360
living towards the sun

1228
00:58:38,719 --> 00:58:39,039
Right?

1229
00:58:39,039 --> 00:58:41,079
They say in the eyes of every sunflower

1230
00:58:41,079 --> 00:58:41,880
there is a sun

1231
00:58:42,360 --> 00:58:43,559
But I believe my mom

1232
00:58:43,559 --> 00:58:44,679
definitely isn't that cliché

1233
00:58:45,280 --> 00:58:47,639
She must know her son loves sunflower seeds

1234
00:58:48,159 --> 00:58:49,880
and believes these seeds must be super tasty, right?

1235
00:58:50,480 --> 00:58:51,719
When the time comes, those seeds

1236
00:58:51,719 --> 00:58:52,880
will be passed into the

1237
00:58:52,880 --> 00:58:53,960
palms and teeth of people worldwide

1238
00:58:54,559 --> 00:58:55,360
You're so annoying
